data.description: Live in Kyle, a fast growing city with so much to offer. It sits in between Austin and all the beautiful rivers and wine country. Choose your destination! This immaculate one-story home is located in Meadows of Kyle and it has so much charm! As you enter the home you will find yourself in an open floor plan that will impress. The kitchen is spacious with enough to host your beautiful dining table. It also offers granite countertops, a built-in microwave, a gas range and a breakfast bar. Relax and reset in the primary bedroom that is so spacious! Enjoy your primary bathroom that has a lovely walk in shower and a walk in closet. Enjoy the luxury of a carpet free home that boasts laminate wood floors and tile. The backyard has a sweet deck that is perfect for a BBQ or just to relax. This community has its very own pool that is on the same street as this home. The sidewalks throughout make it so nice to take walks. This neighborhood is very close to I-35 so you will not have a long way to get to the highway for your commute or to enjoy all the restaurants and shopping nearby. It really does not get any better than this. Don’t miss out on this stunning home, schedule your private tour today!
